'''加布里埃尔·多斯桑托斯·马加良斯'''（{{lang-pt|Gabriel dos Santos Magalhães}}，{{IPA-pt|ˌɡabɾiˈɛw dus ˈsɐ̃tus mɐɣɐˈʎɐ̃js}}，{{bd|1997年|12月19日|}}），是一名[[巴西|巴西]]職業足球員，現時效力[[英格蘭超級足球聯賽|英格蘭超級足球聯賽]]球隊[[阿仙奴足球會|阿仙奴]]。司職[[中堅|中堅]]。

== 球會生涯 ==
=== 阿瓦伊 ===
馬加希斯於[[巴西|巴西]][[聖保羅_(巴西)|聖保羅]]出生。13歲時，他乘坐12小時的巴士前往[[弗洛里亚诺波利斯|弗洛里亚诺波利斯]]，準備於[[阿瓦伊足球俱乐部|艾華爾]]開始其職業生涯。但馬加希斯因思鄉而於一星期後返回聖保羅。兩星期後，他重新考慮後決定返回，並最終於16歲時簽下首份職業合同<ref>{{Cite web|title=PROSPECT {{!}} Gabriel Magalhães {{!}} Get French Football News|url=https://www.getfootballnewsfrance.com/2020/prospect-gabriel-magalhaes/|access-date=2020-08-28|website=www.getfootballnewsfrance.com|language=en|archive-date=2020-05-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200510085723/https://www.getfootballnewsfrance.com/2020/prospect-gabriel-magalhaes/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2017年，他隨隊升班至[[巴西足球甲級聯賽|巴西足球甲級聯賽]]<ref>{{Cite web|last=|first=|date=2017-04-25|title=Avaí Futebol Clube » Gabriel|url= https://web.archive.org/web/20170425012542/http://www.avai.com.br/novo/jogadores/gabriel-dos-santos-magalhaes|archive-url=|archive-date=|access-date=2020-08-28|website=web.archive.org|language=Pt}}</ref>。

=== 里爾 ===
2017年1月31日，馬加希斯轉會至[[法國甲組足球聯賽|法國甲組足球聯賽]]球隊[[里爾奧林匹克體育會|里爾]]，簽約4年半<ref name=":0">{{Cite web|title=Gabriel Magalhaes: Who is Arsenal's new signing? Why is he so highly rated?|url=https://www.skysports.com/football/news/11095/11964146/gabriel-magalhaes-who-is-arsenals-new-signing-why-is-he-so-highly-rated|access-date=2020-08-28|website=Sky Sports|language=en|archive-date=2020-08-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200830120202/https://www.skysports.com/football/news/11095/11964146/gabriel-magalhaes-who-is-arsenals-new-signing-why-is-he-so-highly-rated|dead-url=no}}</ref>。他為里爾B隊上陣數場後，先被外借至[[馬些路·比爾沙|-{zh-hans:马塞洛·贝尔萨;zh-hk:馬些路·比爾沙;zh-tw:馬塞洛·貝爾薩;}-]]執教的[[特魯瓦足球俱樂部|托耶]]<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.unibet.co.uk/blog/football/ligue-1/how-lille%E2%80%99s-gabriel-became-one-of-europe%E2%80%99s-most-coveted-young-centre-backs-1.1418748|title=How Lille’s Gabriel became one of Europe’s most coveted young centre-backs|publisher= Unibet|accessdate= 2020-09-01|language= en}}</ref>，再被外借至[[克罗地亚足球甲级联赛|克罗地亚足球甲级联赛]]的球隊[[萨格勒布迪纳摩足球俱乐部|薩格勒布戴拿模]]，於兩隊的一線隊各上陣1次<ref>{{cite web|url= https://www.losc.fr/joueur/losc-gabriel-dos-santos-magalhaes-2019-2020|title= Gabriel dos Santos Magalhães|publisher= Lille OSC|accessdate= 2020-02-03|language= Fr|archive-date= 2020-03-31|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20200331110120/https://www.losc.fr/joueur/losc-gabriel-dos-santos-magalhaes-2019-2020|dead-url= yes}}</ref>。2018年，馬加希斯返回里爾，於2月10日對陣[[甘岡前進會|甘岡]]的比賽中首次為球隊上陣。全季他共為球隊上陣14次，並於對陣[[巴黎圣日耳曼足球俱乐部|巴黎圣日耳曼]]時攻入首個入球，助球隊以5比1勝出<ref name=":1">{{Cite web|title=Brazil - Gabriel - Profile with news, career statistics and history - Soccerway|url=https://us.soccerway.com/players/gabriel-dos-santos-magalhaes/433485/|access-date=2020-08-28|website=us.soccerway.com|language=en|archive-date=2020-09-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200912035221/https://us.soccerway.com/players/gabriel-dos-santos-magalhaes/433485/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

次季，馬加希斯的上陣時間增加，與[[何塞·馮特|-{zh-cn:若泽·丰特; zh-tw:何塞·馮特; zh-hk:荷西·方迪;}-]]組成中堅防線。於[[2019–20年歐洲冠軍聯賽|2019–20年歐洲冠軍聯賽]]小組賽，他上陣了全部6場比賽<ref>{{Cite web|date=2020-08-23|title=Meet the towering Lille defender on his way to Arsenal|url=https://inews.co.uk/sport/football/gabriel-magalhaes-lille-arsenal-transfer-news-everton-man-utd-defender-572254|access-date=2020-08-24|website=inews.co.uk|language=en|archive-date=2020-09-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200914223853/https://inews.co.uk/sport/football/gabriel-magalhaes-lille-arsenal-transfer-news-everton-man-utd-defender-572254|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== 阿仙奴 ===
2020年9月1日，馬加希斯轉會至[[英格蘭超級足球聯賽|英格蘭超級足球聯賽]]球隊[[阿仙奴足球會|阿仙奴]]<ref>{{Cite web|title=Gabriel is a Gunner! {{!}} Defender joins Arsenal|url=https://www.arsenal.com/news/gabriel-gunner-defender-joins-arsenal|access-date=2020-09-01|website=Arsenal.com|language=en|date=2020-09-01|archive-date=2020-09-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200901153453/https://www.arsenal.com/news/gabriel-gunner-defender-joins-arsenal|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。有數間球會對他有意，出價亦符合里爾的要求<ref>{{Cite web|title=Gabriel Magalhaes set to join Arsenal after £27m fee agreed with Lille|url=https://www.skysports.com/football/news/11670/12051569/gabriel-magalhaes-set-to-join-arsenal-after-27m-fee-agreed-with-lille|access-date=2020-09-10|website=Sky Sports|language=en|archive-date=2020-08-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200825012828/https://www.skysports.com/football/news/11670/12051569/gabriel-magalhaes-set-to-join-arsenal-after-27m-fee-agreed-with-lille|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Gabriel Magalhaes to Arsenal: The making of the Brazilian at Avai|url=https://www.skysports.com/football/story-telling/11095/12060865/gabriel-magalhaes-to-arsenal-the-making-of-the-brazilian-at-avai|access-date=2020-09-10|website=Sky Sports|language=en|archive-date=2020-09-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200901204559/https://www.skysports.com/football/story-telling/11095/12060865/gabriel-magalhaes-to-arsenal-the-making-of-the-brazilian-at-avai|dead-url=no}}</ref>。阿仙奴最終成功以2700萬鎊（包含浮動條款）的價錢買下他<ref>{{Cite news|title=Arsenal sign defender Gabriel from Lille|language=en|work=BBC Sport|url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/53990363|access-date=2020-09-10|archive-date=2020-09-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200906035620/https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/53990363|dead-url=no}}</ref>。9月12日，馬加希斯於聯賽第1輪客勝[[富咸足球會|富咸]]3比0的比賽中，首次上陣並攻入1球<ref>{{Cite news|last=Begley|first=Emlyn|title=Fulham 0-3 Arsenal: Gabriel & Willian impress on debut in Gunners win|work=BBC Sport|url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/53990363|date=2020-09-12|access-date=2020-09-12|language=en|archive-date=2020-09-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200917014356/https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/53990363|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2021年3月11日，馬加希斯在[[2020–21年歐霸盃淘汰賽|歐洲聯賽十六強賽]]對陣[[奥林匹亚科斯足球俱乐部|奧林匹亞科斯]]的比賽中踢進在[[歐足總歐洲聯賽|歐足總歐洲聯賽]]的首球，幫助球隊以3-1獲勝。<ref>{{cite web |title=Olympiacos 1-3 Arsenal: Gabriel And Mohamed Elneny Strike Late To Give Mikel Arteta's Team The Edge |url=https://www.outlookindia.com/website/story/sports-news-olympiacos-1-3-arsenal-gabriel-and-mohamed-elneny-strike-late-to-give-mikel-artetas-team-the-edge/376914 |publisher=Outlook |date=2021-03-12 |accessdate=2021-03-12 |archive-date=2021-03-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210316124152/https://www.outlookindia.com/website/story/sports-news-olympiacos-1-3-arsenal-gabriel-and-mohamed-elneny-strike-late-to-give-mikel-artetas-team-the-edge/376914 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

== 國家隊生涯 ==
馬加希斯曾代表{{link-en|巴西20歲以下國家足球隊|Brazil national under-20 football team|巴西 U20}}參加{{link-en|2017年南美洲青年足球錦標賽|2017 South American U-20 Championship}}<ref>{{Soccerway|gabriel-dos-santos-magalhaes/433485}}</ref>。他原本將會入選[[巴西23歲以下國家足球隊|巴西23歲以下國家足球隊]]出戰[[2020年夏季奥林匹克运动会|2020年夏季奥林匹克运动会]]，但賽事因[[2019冠状病毒病疫情|2019冠状病毒病疫情]]而延後至2021年<ref name=":0" />。

